{"tid":2162151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中鐵建董事長陳奮健「不幸逝世」 國資委巡視組剛完成檢查","createTime":"2020-08-18T03:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T00:33:49.000Z","uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"869946c4878818287a0733b47b023f838a9e6849","tid":2162151,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"中國鐵道建築集團公司董事長兼黨委書記陳奮健逝世，終年57歲。<br />\n<br />\n中國鐵建公告指，陳奮健自2018年起任中國鐵建董事長、執行董事、黨委書記及董事會提名委員會主席，公司對其不幸逝世表示沉痛的哀悼。目前，公司的生產經營情況一切正常，公司將在合理可行的情況下盡快委任適當人選，以符合公司章程的要求，公司將於適當時候另行刊發公告。<br />\n<br />\n57歲的陳奮健，曾任職中國交通建設副董事長兼總經理，兩年前轉任中鐵建高層，最近一次公開露面，是上星期四到河北雄安新區考察。"},{"pid":"cf598123e5fe0b742cc011557edb3192dc6cfcdf","tid":2162151,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"幾時到被裁者聯盟「被」跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de09e575c9adecfa41cb47c878e7779f50c3330d","tid":2162151,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:50:00.000Z","msg":"澎湃新聞引述內部人士指， 陳奮健是墮樓身亡。"},{"pid":"7a51b052d7e83634ae0eb4b835f7b9de9b696b16","tid":2162151,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"只有死人才最守秘密，一人保全黨"},{"pid":"6bb37c8c9fc4c35124713bb004997ff85128d7ec","tid":2162151,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:51:33.000Z","msg":"被不幸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1995353/org/5d36db11dd2d4a2212f67dadd728271b.jpg/k8qCvqSlrBEAScEw1SKcD7alHKbuIJPLJEoTCSRKEwk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1995353%2Forg%2F5d36db11dd2d4a2212f67dadd728271b.jpg%2Fk8qCvqSlrBEAScEw1SKcD7alHKbuIJPLJEoTCSRKEwk&h=44f93abb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2115074c87da477668972a0f30ceeb582c477a63","tid":2162151,"uid":12558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2